               <p>Court. Look at the prisoner, do you remember his conviction? - He was capitally convicted in July 1782, I brought him to the bar, for I remember his accepting the King's pardon upon condition of being transported, I delivered him and others on the 11th of January on board the hulks.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830910-13-person175">
